'''
== Ditlamorago tsa go dirisa  ditagi ==
'''<br />
<br />
Tiriso ya  ditagi tse di seng ka fa molaong wa lefatshe la [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Botswana Botswana] jaaka motekwane, [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cocaine Cocaine],[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Methaqualone Mandrax],tick,heroine, crack,[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ecstasy Ecstasy],methylated spirit le glue e diphatsa mo botsogong.<br />
''Ditlamorago tsa go dirisa ditagi''<br />
* Go feroga sebete<br />
* Matlho a a kgaletseng madi<br />
* Go fokotsa kgonagalo ya tsholo<br />
* Go nna le bolwetse jwa madi a matona<br />
* Go thorega boroko<br />
* Go lebala mo go sa tlwaelesegang<br />
* Go bona dilo tse di seyong<br />
* Go sitwa, mogote o o kwa godimo le go fufula<br />
* go roroma<br />
* Go thulana ga meno mo go sa laolesegeng<br />
* Go gogega ga ditshika tsa mmele<br />
* pono e e letobo<br />
* Kgotlholo e e sa foleng<br />
* Koketsego ya kgonagalo ya go tsenwa ke kankere ya mahatlha, molomo, mometso le loleme.<br />
<br />
''
=== Ke ka lemoga jang fa mongwe mo lelwapeng a na le mathata a ditagi? ===
''<br />
* Go fetoga ga maikutlo mo nakong e khutshwane, go didimala thata, kana go bua thata kana go tshega go sena se se kgatlhang.<br />
* Go nna matlhagatlhaga o ipona o le wena fela.<br />
* Go nna o ikgogonne.<br />
* Go nna mo dikolotong mo go bakiwang ke go reka ditagi kgotsa go duela dikatlholo tsa semolao.
<br />
* Go kgopisega motlhofo kgotsa go ganela fa go umakiwa tiriso ditagi ga gagwe.<br />
* Go sa tseye karolo mo mererong ya tsamaiso ya lelwapa.
<br />
* Go lofa kwa sekolong, tirong ga mmogo le ko lwapeng.<br />
* Go sa itlhokomela sentle.<br />
* Go sa nne le lenyora la go atlega mo go sepe.<br />
* Go tlhoka go dira sentle kwa sekoleng kgotsa kwa tirong.<br />
* Go nna o faraferwe ke mathata a se-molao; tiriso ya ditagi ga e letelesege ka jalo badirise ba tsone ba nna fela mo diatleng tsa ba se-molao mo go akaretsang le go tsena mo kgolegelong.
